{"tid":1849781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柴灣警察宿舍兩警員家屬發燒　男警同被送院檢查","createTime":"2020-01-29T08:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T09:52:47.000Z","uid":184679,"like":197,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"b60285171bcc97bdfca6f840d344603674cf4d81","tid":1849781,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:31:42.000Z","msg":"網上流傳今（29日）凌晨曾有全副防護裝備醫護人員，到柴灣已婚警察宿舍帶走3人，到東區醫院隔離檢查。警方今午向本報確認事件，指出該宿舍內一名隸屬西區警區男警的兩名家屬發燒，雖然男警並無出現病徵，但3人同被送院，正等候測試結果。警方表示，宿舍已徹底清潔和消毒，並提醒人員注意個人衛生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200129/s00001/63a78c65b6b5a4025414bdf43144caff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200129%2Fs00001%2F63a78c65b6b5a4025414bdf43144caff.jpg&h=350df635&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200129/s00001/1580285719175/【武漢肺炎】柴灣警察宿舍兩警員家屬發燒-男警同被送院檢查\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200129%2Fs00001%2F1580285719175%2F%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E6%9F%B4%E7%81%A3%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E5%85%A9%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E7%99%BC%E7%87%92-%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E5%90%8C%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E6%AA%A2%E6%9F%A5&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=e76d4e0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200129%2Fs00001%2F1580285719175%2F%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E6%9F%B4%E7%81%A3%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E5%85%A9%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E7%99%BC%E7%87%92-%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E5%90%8C%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E6%AA%A2%E6%9F%A5&h=4d602e8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200129/s00001/1580285719175/【武漢肺炎】柴灣警察宿舍兩警員家屬發燒-男警同被送院檢查</a>"},{"pid":"1cc0a508d255334ff48af30acd346e0b9b831d35","tid":1849781,"uid":103405,"like":4,"dislike